'''挪威牛油危機'''（{{lang-en|Norwegian butter crisis}}）是由在2011年下旬期间[[挪威|挪威]]境內[[黄油|牛油]]供應短缺及價格急升的現象。這次的牛油荒歸咎於天氣因素、挪威政府對[[奶製品|奶製品]]的入口限制以及該國漸漸改變的[[飲食習慣|飲食習慣]]。這危機終使得牛油價格暴升，甚至與銀價看齊，並造成4.3千萬克朗的經濟損失。民眾因而要求政府改革現有的農業政策。

==成因==
挪威人素有於[[聖誕節|聖誕節]]前製作至少7種糕點的[[習俗|習俗]]，寓意能渡過甜蜜聖誕，這傳統增加了對牛油的需求<ref name="ming">{{cite news|title=挪威牛油荒 500克炒至4000元|url=http://www.mpfinance.com/htm/Finance/20111215/News/ad_tbx1.htm|3=|work=明報|date=2011-12-15|accessdate=1-9-2015|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304204603/http://www.mpfinance.com/htm/Finance/20111215/News/ad_tbx1.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。然而，2011年夏季的大雨令動物飼料失收，[[牛奶|牛奶]]產量較去年大減2千萬公升，牛油價格開始上漲<ref name="Guardian">{{cite news|title=Butter shortage puts the knife into Norwegian Christmas plans|url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2011/dec/14/norwegian-butter-crisis-shortage-christmas|last=Andersen|first=Audrey|work=The Guardian|date=2011-12-14|accessdate=2012-01-01|archive-date=2013-04-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130425080602/http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2011/dec/14/norwegian-butter-crisis-shortage-christmas|dead-url=no}}</ref>。隨著聖誕節即將到來，人們開始大量購買牛油。同時，挪威近年興起的[[低碳水化合物飲食|低碳水化合物飲食]]更令大眾對牛油的需求有增無減<ref name="Telegraph" />。一份統計指，在2010年至2011年間，民眾對於牛油的需求就增加了三成<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.metro.co.uk/news/884900-norway-butter-crisis-spreads-as-nation-consumes-entire-stock|title=Norway butter crisis spreads as nation consumes entire stock|work=Metro|date=2011-12-14|accessdate=2011-11-28|archive-date=2012-12-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121204042224/http://www.metro.co.uk/news/884900-norway-butter-crisis-spreads-as-nation-consumes-entire-stock|dead-url=no}}</ref>。這種種的因素令牛油的銷量快速增長﹕在10月，該國的牛油銷售量上升20%，而在11月更增至30%<ref name="Telegraph">{{cite news|title=Norway butter shortage: 'margarine is just not the same'|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/foodanddrink/foodanddrinkvideo/8955731/Norway-butter-shortage-margarine-is-just-not-the-same.html|work=The Daily Telegraph|date=2011-12-14|accessdate=2012-01-01|archive-date=2020-06-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200610170102/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/foodanddrink/foodanddrinkvideo/8955731/Norway-butter-shortage-margarine-is-just-not-the-same.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

在需求上升的同時，市場的運作更加劇這場牛油荒。挪威企業Tine幾乎[[壟斷|壟斷]]全國的牛油供應，該國近九成的牛油也是由他們生產的<ref name="Scotsman">{{cite news|title=Spreading butter crisis forces cut in import tax|url=http://www.scotsman.com/news/international/spreading_butter_crisis_forces_cut_in_import_tax_1_2008834|work=The Scotsman|date=2011-12-15|accessdate=2012-01-01|archive-date=2012-01-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120110191728/http://www.scotsman.com/news/international/spreading_butter_crisis_forces_cut_in_import_tax_1_2008834|dead-url=no}}</ref>。儘管如此，由於這企業未有事前通知奶農增加產量和過度出口的關係，他們所生產的牛油還是未能滿足本地需求<ref name="Guardian" />。據報導，挪威每日的牛油[[經濟短缺|短缺量]]為500至1000噸<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.thenational.ae/lifestyle/norwegian-butter-crisis-churns-up-christmas-shortages|title=Norwegian butter crisis churns up Christmas shortages|last=Langton|first=James|work=The National|location=Abu Dhabi|date=2011-12-17|accessdate=2011-12-28|archive-date=2016-06-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160606135509/http://www.thenational.ae/lifestyle/norwegian-butter-crisis-churns-up-christmas-shortages|dead-url=no}}</ref>。另一方面，自[[二次大戰|二次大戰]]起，政府為保障本地農民的利益而向進口的奶製品設立高昂的[[關稅|關稅]]，這措施令挪威市面上的牛油大多由本地供應，而進口的牛油價格則极高<ref>{{cite news|url=http://blogs.wsj.com/source/2011/12/19/norway-embarrassed-by-butter-shortage/|title=Norway: Embarrassed By Butter Shortage|last=Hovland|first=Kjetil Malkenes|work=The Wall Street Journal|date=2011-12-19|accessdate=2011-12-28|archive-date=2019-12-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191206141157/https://blogs.wsj.com/source/2011/12/19/norway-embarrassed-by-butter-shortage/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在12月中，250克的丹麥牛油市值300[[克朗|克朗]]（約50[[美元|美元]]）<ref>{{cite news |title=Et kilo smør koster nu over 1000 kroner |url=http://www.bt.dk/udland/et-kilo-smoer-koster-nu-over-1000-kroner |last=Kirkbak |first=Jesper |language=da |work=B.T |date=11-12-2011 |accessdate=6-1-2012 |archive-date=2020-11-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201117202306/https://www.bt.dk/udland/et-kilo-smoer-koster-nu-over-1000-kroner |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==反應及後果==
牛油的奇缺使該產品的價格暴漲，報導指有人願意以與銀價看齊的3000克朗（約500美元）來購買500克的牛油，亦有人從德國偷運90公斤牛油入境而被捕<ref name="ming"/>。為解決這場危機，Tine要求挪威政府降低關稅以進口更多牛油<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.newsinenglish.no/2011/12/08/calls-rise-to-bust-butter-monopoly/ |title=Calls rise to bust butter ‘monopoly’ |last=Berglund |first=Nina |publisher=newsinenglish.no |date=8-12-2011 |accessdate=2011-12-28 |archive-date=2021-01-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210125234929/https://www.newsinenglish.no/2011/12/08/calls-rise-to-bust-butter-monopoly/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，奥斯陆地区的挪威民众大都越境赴瑞典采购<ref name="mofcom">{{cite news|url=http://www.mofcom.gov.cn/article/i/jyjl/m/201112/20111207867401.shtml |title=挪威紧缺黄油 |publisher=中华人民共和国商务部网站 |date=2011-12-07}}</ref>，一些挪威民众甚至要求其在冰岛的亲戚朋友采取邮寄黄油的方式来应对<ref name="mofcom"/>。隨後，奧斯陸政府決定把關稅從每克25克朗下調至4克朗<ref name="wsj">{{cite news|url=http://online.wsj.com/article/SB10001424052970204553904577102332973418996.html|title=As National Butter Shortage Bites, Norwegians Get Churning|last=Malkenes Hovland|first=Kjetil|work=The Wall Street Journal|date=2011-12-19|accessdate=2011-12-28|archive-date=2013-01-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130109172826/http://online.wsj.com/article/SB10001424052970204553904577102332973418996.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。不過，這政策的成效受到質疑，Tine的發言人指牛油的供應量要到翌年1月才回復正常<ref name="Scotsman" />。

鄰國[[瑞典|瑞典]]試圖協助挪威化解這場危機，瑞典的一些[[超級市場|超級市場]]宣佈只要挪威的民眾願意到其門市，他們就會提供免費的牛油<ref>{{cite news|title=Butter shortage takes the biscuit in Norway|url=http://www.irishtimes.com/newspaper/world/2011/1220/1224309294257.html|last=Andersen|first=Audrey|work=The Irish Times|date=2011-12-20|accessdate=2012-01-01|archive-date=2011-12-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111221040747/http://www.irishtimes.com/newspaper/world/2011/1220/1224309294257.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。奶製品商人卡爾·克里斯汀·蘭德指示其公司須增加[[奧斯陸|奧斯陸]]和[[克里斯蒂安桑|克里斯蒂安桑]]的牛油供應<ref name="Guardian" />。在瑞典東南部接壤城鎮{{link-en|斯維納松德|Svinesund}}，商舖大幅增加牛油的供應量，數量為平常的20倍<ref>{{cite news|title=Swedes in Norwegian butter smuggling bust|url=http://www.thelocal.se/38022/20111219/|work=The Local|date=2011-12-19|accessdate=2012-01-01|archive-date=2012-01-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120107225222/http://www.thelocal.se/38022/20111219|dead-url=no}}</ref>。同時，丹麥製作電視節目呼籲國民向挪威捐贈牛油。最終，電視台替他們的鄰國籌得4000包牛油<ref name="Scotsman" />。丹麥的跨境機場和碼頭[[免稅店|免稅店]]設置大量牛油存貨供挪威人購買<ref>{{cite news|url=http://edition.cnn.com/2011/12/13/world/europe/norway-butter-shortage/?hpt=wo_bn9|title=Prices spike as butter shortage spreads through Norway|last=Mellingsater|first=Olaf|publisher=CNN|date=2011-12-13|accessdate=2012-01-01|archive-date=2016-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160308040103/http://edition.cnn.com/2011/12/13/world/europe/norway-butter-shortage/?hpt=wo_bn9|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

牛油危機還觸發人們對政治的不滿。有挪威民眾指責Tine壟斷本地市場，促請政府改革<ref>{{cite news|title=A bitter search for butter|url=http://www.ottawacitizen.com/business/bitter+search+butter/5861882/story.html|last=Charter|first=David|work=The Times|date=2011-12-14|accessdate=2012-01-01}}{{dead link|date=2017年12月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>。[[右翼|右翼]]組織指政府的農業政策失當導致此次的牛油荒<ref name="ming"/>。這場的危機終造成4.3千萬克朗的經濟損失，[[挪威進步黨|進步黨]]因而要求壟斷市場的Tine為此負責任<ref>[http://www.tnp.no/norway/economy/2782-frp-requires-tine-to-pay-for-butter-crisis-in-norway FrP Requires Tine to Pay for Butter Crisis in Norway] {{Wayback|url=http://www.tnp.no/norway/economy/2782-frp-requires-tine-to-pay-for-butter-crisis-in-norway |date=20210123041406 }}, 12-3-2012</ref>。

